main event: A civilian observed 3 objects moving in a straight line in a westerly direction over Anchorage, Alaska, on 20 July 1952.
interesting points: The objects emitted a reddish glow and were round in shape,The sighting lasted for approximately 10 minutes,An investigation revealed no additional information or physical evidence,Another report mentions a bright light observed by a civilian on 30 March 1953,The possibility exists that the observed light could have been planet Jupiter.
sighted object: three round objects emitting a reddish glow
